The fix replaces regex-based extraction with `xml.etree.ElementTree`:
- Walks all `<w:p>` elements in document order (including those nested in `<w:tbl>/<w:tr>/<w:tc>`), preserving paragraph/table reading order.
- Concatenates descendant `<w:t>` text per paragraph, with entities automatically decoded (`&amp;` → `&`).
- Joins paragraph texts with `\n`.
